6
00:00:18,770 --> 00:00:21,570
Tapi selama syuting,

7
00:00:21,570 --> 00:00:25,370
produser Tn. Takashi Harawaki tewas.

8
00:00:25,370 --> 00:00:29,270
Karena video dirinya yang sedang meminum racun dan sesuatu

9
00:00:29,270 --> 00:00:31,870
