12
00:00:38,770 --> 00:00:40,670
Joji Naito.

13
00:00:40,670 --> 00:00:42,870
Siapa dia?

14
00:00:42,870 --> 00:00:45,170
Dia adalah presiden dari klub horor

15
00:00:45,170 --> 00:00:47,870
